episodes.title: Good News, Bad News
episodes.plot: Jerry and George argue whether an overnight visitor Jerry is expecting is coming with romantic intentions.

episodes.title: The Stakeout
episodes.plot: Jerry and George stake out the lobby of an office building to find a woman Jerry met at a party but whose name and phone number he didn't get.

episodes.title: The Robbery
episodes.plot: After Jerry's apartment is robbed, Jerry starts to look for other apartments. But Jerry and George both want the same apartment, and Elaine wants the apartment of whoever loses out.

episodes.title: Male Unbonding
episodes.plot: Jerry tries various excuses to avoid meeting with an old friend with whom he no longer shares any interests.

episodes.title: The Stock Tip
episodes.plot: Jerry becomes apprehensive when he and George buy stock and the price falls while the person who suggested the stock is in hospital and can't tell them when to sell.
